Hello dear fragrance family and everyone else. 💫💞🩵🛟⚓️🛟🩵💞💫 As you know, I'm still on my break and am enjoying my vacation to the fullest 👍💯🛟🩵⚓️. I hope you are all doing well and you are healthy.  Here's a little insight into the first 3 days of my vacation, I'm very happy.  We were in Lühe, I went shopping and yesterday we were on Sylt.  Of course I had to visit a perfumery again and left it full of joy.  Today we went for a stroll in Stade and are still invited.  I'll continue to enjoy my time off, it's really good for me.  I continue to enjoy my vacation.  Please take care everyone 🙏 until we meet again at the end of September and I really hope you understand me.  Many greetings and hugs Reni ❤️🫶❤️ #Klamotten

Todays Fashion Statement 
-Where’s my tan?????????

This mornings luxury is reserved for some time in the sun. My outfit, the perfect bikini for the perfect tan. Well, at least that’s the plan.

Most summers my go-to tanning spot is South Florida. This year however I’ve had alot of summer traveling up north; Canada, Minnesota & few more beautiful places. Next up for September is Germany and some time back home in Sweden. 

So for the rest of the weekend my primary goal is to become “human bacon.” Ok, well maybe that’s a little dramatic… Perhaps just a little “baking.”

Enjoy your weeks.

I am Helena of Sweden
